ARInvoiceBasicProcessing_ST is a SecurityClass
	description is "Basic Receivable Invoices Processing"
	Access Rights

		ar Module
			is accessible
				for all actions
				unconditionally

		idm Module
			is accessible
				for all actions
				unconditionally

		CompanyCustomer BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for ReleaseInvoiceObligationGrouping,
					ClearFilter, UpdateFilters, UpdatePaymentCode, 
					ReleaseMyInvoiceObligationGrouping, RefreshData
				when (SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)

		CompanyCustomerComment BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for CreateTransactionComment, Update
				when (Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)

		CompanyCustomerCommentAttachment BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for all actions
					excluding Purge
				when (Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)

		Customer BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for UpdatePaymentCode
				when (CustomerGroup.CustomerGroupAllowsAccess)

		NationalAccountTransaction BusinessClass
			is accessible
